+# Gemini Scheduler
+
+A scheduling application built with modern technologies.
+
+## Description
+
+This project is a scheduler application designed to help manage appointments, meetings, and other time-based events efficiently.
+
+## Features
+
+- Event scheduling and management
+- Calendar integration
+- User-friendly interface
+- Real-time updates
+
+## Installation
+
+```bash
+git clone https://github.com/yourusername/gemini-scheduler.git
+cd gemini-scheduler
+npm install
+```
+
+## Usage
+
+```bash
+npm start
+```
+
+## Contributing
+
+1. Fork the repository
+2. Create your feature branch (`git checkout -b feature/amazing-feature`)
+3. Commit your changes (`git commit -m 'Add some amazing feature'`)
+4. Push to the branch (`git push origin feature/amazing-feature`)
+5. Open a Pull Request
